Authentication Navigation Tests
===============================
     
Navigate Between Authentication Screens Test
-------------------------------------------------------------------
* Workplace URL screen should be displayed
* Connect button should be disabled
* Enter a valid Workspace URL
* Connect button should be enabled
* Click the Connect button
* Authentication Selection screen should be displayed
* Click the Login button
* Login screen should be displayed
* Click the Create an account button on the Login screen
* Sign Up screen should be displayed
* Click the Back button on the Sign Up screen
* Login screen should be displayed

Remember Workspace Test
-------------------------------------------------------------------
* Workplace URL screen should be displayed
* Connect button should be disabled
* Enter a valid Workspace URL
* Connect button should be enabled
* Click the Connect button
* Relaunch app with no reset
* Authentication Selection screen should be displayed
* Verify the Workspace URL on the Authentication Selection screen